{"name": "Fish, Inc. Dunellen Area", "alternate_name": "", "description": "New clients must call for an appointment 732
356-0081. Walk-ins cannot be accommodated.  
Food Room: Open Mondays, Wednesdays, and Fridays, 9 a.m.-12 noon and the third Saturday of 
each month, 9 a.m.-11 a.m. (excluding July & August). Limited capacity, arrive early. Clients are 
limited to once a month service and must show proof of residency in Piscataway, Dunellen, 
Middlesex, South Plainfield, Edison, Highland Park or Green Brook. Must show proof of need (eg. 
TANF, SSI, WIC, FOOD STAMPS, MEDICAID, DISABILITY, WELFARE, UNEMPLOYMENT 
COMPENSATION) or show proof of low household income not in excess of Federal Guidelines. 
Canned and refrigerated food donations, personal care products and pet food accepted. 
Fishes & Loaves Cafe: Free, home-cooked dinners for anyone in need the third Friday of each 
month (excluding July & August). Eat-In the cafe 6:00 p.m.-7:00 p.m. or take-out meals.  Held at the 
former school cafeteria at Our Lady of Fatima RC Church, New Market Road, Piscataway.  All are 
welcome!
